@page "/security"

<PageTitle>Security & Privacy — PdfToolStack</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="How PdfToolStack handles document security, including encrypted transfers, temporary processing, automatic deletion, account data, and support contacts." />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://pdftoolstack.com/security" />
</HeadContent>

<div class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container" style="max-width:860px;">

        <div class="legal-header" style="text-align:center;padding-bottom:2rem;">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">🔒</div>
            <h1>Your documents are safe with us</h1>
            <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:1.1rem;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;">
                We built PdfToolStack with privacy as the default —
                not an afterthought. Here's exactly how we protect
                your files and data.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust badges row -->
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:3rem;">

            <div class="sign-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;">
                <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">⏱️</div>
                <h3 style="font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Auto-deleted in 1 hour</h3>
                <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--text-secondary);">
                    Uploaded and generated files are designed to
                    be deleted automatically after processing,
                    typically within 1 hour.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="sign-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;">
                <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🔐</div>
                <h3 style="font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Encrypted in transit</h3>
                <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--text-secondary);">
                    All file transfers use TLS 1.2+ encryption.
                    Your documents are never sent unencrypted.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="sign-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;">
                <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🚫</div>
                <h3 style="font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Privacy-minded analytics</h3>
                <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--text-secondary);">
                    Core PDF tools do not require advertising
                    cookies, and analytics should not include
                    file contents.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="sign-card" style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem;">
                <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🏢</div>
                <h3 style="font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Cloud infrastructure</h3>
                <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:var(--text-secondary);">
                    Built on managed cloud services with operational
                    controls for reliability and document workflows.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="legal-content">

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>🗂️ File handling</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Files are uploaded over an encrypted
                        HTTPS connection directly to our
                        processing service for the requested
                        workflow.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        After processing, your output file is
                        temporarily stored on Microsoft Azure
                        Blob Storage so you can download it.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Files are designed to be deleted
                        automatically after processing, typically
                        within <strong>1 hour</strong> of upload.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        File processing is automated. Support staff
                        do not need your file contents for routine
                        troubleshooting.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        We do not read, analyze, index, or
                        train AI models on the contents of
                        your documents.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>🤖 AI tools and your documents</h2>
                <p>
                    When you use AI-powered tools such as the
                    AI Contract Reviewer or Invoice Extractor,
                    your document content is sent to
                    Anthropic's Claude API for processing.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Anthropic does not store or train on
                        API-submitted content per their
                        <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/privacy"
                           target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                            API data usage policy
                        </a>.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        We log only the tool used, token count,
                        and timestamp — never the document
                        content itself.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        We recommend not uploading documents
                        containing highly sensitive personal
                        data (e.g. passports, medical records)
                        to AI tools.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>🔑 Authentication and accounts</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Authentication is handled by
                        <strong>Auth0</strong>, an
                        industry-leading identity platform
                        trusted by thousands of companies.
                        We never store your password.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        You can sign in with Google, GitHub,
                        Microsoft, Facebook, or LinkedIn —
                        your credentials stay with those
                        providers.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        You can delete your account and all
                        associated data at any time from your
                        <a href="/account">Account page</a>.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>💳 Payments</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Payments are processed by
                        <strong>Stripe</strong>, a PCI DSS
                        Level 1 certified payment processor.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        We never see, store, or have access
                        to your credit card details.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Your billing information is stored
                        securely by Stripe under their
                        <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy"
                           target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                            privacy policy
                        </a>.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>🏗️ Infrastructure</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        PdfToolStack runs on
                        <strong>Microsoft Azure</strong>
                        in the West US 2 region.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Our API enforces HTTPS-only connections
                        with HSTS headers in production.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        We use rate limiting, magic byte
                        validation on all uploads, and
                        Content Security Policy headers to
                        protect against common attacks.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        File size limits and type restrictions
                        are enforced server-side — not just
                        in the browser.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>📋 Compliance</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>GDPR</strong> — We support
                        the right to erasure. You can delete
                        all your data from your
                        <a href="/account/delete">account settings</a>.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>CCPA</strong> — We do not
                        sell personal information.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Cookies</strong> — We use only
                        essential cookies. Core PDF tools do not
                        require advertising cookies.
                        <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2>📬 Security contact</h2>
                <p>
                    Found a security vulnerability? Please
                    report it responsibly to
                    <a href="mailto:security@pdftoolstack.com">
                        security@pdftoolstack.com
                    </a>.
                    We take all reports seriously and aim to
                    respond within 48 hours.
                </p>
            </section>

        </div>

        <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;padding:2rem;background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:12px;">
            <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-secondary);margin-bottom:1rem;">
                Still have questions about how we handle your data?
            </p>
            <a href="mailto:admin@pdftoolstack.com"
               class="download-button"
               style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;">
                Contact us
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
